{"segment_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0001", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction", "source_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《明堂位》 1", "sort_key": "0001", "text_original": "昔者周公朝諸侯于明堂之位：天子負斧依南鄉而立；三公，中階之前，北面東上。諸侯之位，阼階之東，西面北上。諸伯之國，西階之西，東面北上。諸子之國，門東，北面東上。諸男之國，門西，北面東上。九夷之國，東門之外，西面北上。八蠻之國，南門之外，北面東上。六戎之國，西門之外，東面南上。五狄之國，北門之外，南面東上。九采之國，應門之外，北面東上。四塞，世告至。此周公明堂之位也。明堂也者，明諸侯之尊卑也。", "text_normalized": "昔者周公朝諸侯于明堂之位：天子負斧依南鄉而立；三公，中階之前，北面東上。諸侯之位，阼階之東，西面北上。諸伯之國，西階之西，東面北上。諸子之國，門東，北面東上。諸男之國，門西，北面東上。九夷之國，東門之外，西面北上。八蠻之國，南門之外，北面東上。六戎之國，西門之外，東面南上。五狄之國，北門之外，南面東上。九采之國，應門之外，北面東上。四塞，世告至。此周公明堂之位也。明堂也者，明諸侯之尊卑也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0002", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction", "source_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《明堂位》 2", "sort_key": "0002", "text_original": "昔殷紂亂天下，脯鬼侯以饗諸侯。是以周公相武王以伐紂。武王崩，成王幼弱，周公踐天子之位以治天下；六年，朝諸侯於明堂，制禮作樂，頒度量，而天下大服；七年，致政於成王；成王以周公為有勛勞於天下，是以封周公於曲阜，地方七百里，革車千乘，命魯公世世祀周公天以子之禮樂。", "text_normalized": "昔殷紂亂天下，脯鬼侯以饗諸侯。是以周公相武王以伐紂。武王崩，成王幼弱，周公踐天子之位以治天下；六年，朝諸侯於明堂，制禮作樂，頒度量，而天下大服；七年，致政於成王；成王以周公為有勛勞於天下，是以封周公於曲阜，地方七百里，革車千乘，命魯公世世祀周公天以子之禮樂。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0003", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction", "source_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《明堂位》 3", "sort_key": "0003", "text_original": "是以魯君，孟春乘大路，載弧韣；旗十有二旒，日月之章；祀帝于郊，配以后稷。天子之禮也。", "text_normalized": "是以魯君，孟春乘大路，載弧韣；旗十有二旒，日月之章；祀帝于郊，配以后稷。天子之禮也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0004", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction", "source_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 4, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《明堂位》 4", "sort_key": "0004", "text_original": "季夏六月，以禘禮祀周公於大廟，牲用白牡；尊用犧象山罍；郁尊用黃目；灌用玉瓚大圭；薦用玉豆雕篹；爵用玉琖，仍雕，加以璧散璧角；俎用梡嶡；升歌《清廟》，下管《象》；朱干玉戚，冕而舞《大武》；皮弁素積，裼而舞《大夏》。昧，東夷之樂也；《任》，南蠻之樂也。納夷蠻之樂於大廟，言廣魯於天下也。", "text_normalized": "季夏六月，以禘禮祀周公於大廟，牲用白牡；尊用犧象山罍；郁尊用黃目；灌用玉瓚大圭；薦用玉豆雕篹；爵用玉琖，仍雕，加以璧散璧角；俎用梡嶡；升歌《清廟》，下管《象》；朱干玉戚，冕而舞《大武》；皮弁素積，裼而舞《大夏》。昧，東夷之樂也；《任》，南蠻之樂也。納夷蠻之樂於大廟，言廣魯於天下也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0005", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction", "source_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 5, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《明堂位》 5", "sort_key": "0005", "text_original": "君卷冕立於阼，夫人副褘立于房中。君肉袒迎牲于門；夫人薦豆籩。卿、大夫贊君，命婦贊夫人：各揚其職。百官廢職服大刑，而天下大服。", "text_normalized": "君卷冕立於阼，夫人副褘立于房中。君肉袒迎牲于門；夫人薦豆籩。卿、大夫贊君，命婦贊夫人：各揚其職。百官廢職服大刑，而天下大服。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0006", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction", "source_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 6, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《明堂位》 6", "sort_key": "0006", "text_original": "是故，夏礿、秋嘗、冬烝，春社、秋省而遂大蜡，天子之祭也。", "text_normalized": "是故，夏礿、秋嘗、冬烝，春社、秋省而遂大蜡，天子之祭也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0007", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction", "source_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 7, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《明堂位》 7", "sort_key": "0007", "text_original": "大廟，天子明堂。庫門，天子皋門。雉門，天子應門。", "text_normalized": "大廟，天子明堂。庫門，天子皋門。雉門，天子應門。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0008", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction", "source_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 8, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《明堂位》 8", "sort_key": "0008", "text_original": "振木鐸於朝，天子之政也。", "text_normalized": "振木鐸於朝，天子之政也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0009", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction", "source_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 9, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《明堂位》 9", "sort_key": "0009", "text_original": "山節藻梲，復廟重檐，刮楹達鄉，反坫出尊，崇坫康圭，疏屏；天子之廟飾也。", "text_normalized": "山節藻梲，復廟重檐，刮楹達鄉，反坫出尊，崇坫康圭，疏屏；天子之廟飾也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0010", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction", "source_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 10, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《明堂位》 10", "sort_key": "0010", "text_original": "鸞車，有虞氏之路也。鉤車，夏后氏之路也。大路，殷路也。乘路，周路也。", "text_normalized": "鸞車，有虞氏之路也。鉤車，夏后氏之路也。大路，殷路也。乘路，周路也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0011", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction", "source_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 11, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《明堂位》 11", "sort_key": "0011", "text_original": "有虞氏之旗，夏后氏之綏，殷之大白，周之大赤。", "text_normalized": "有虞氏之旗，夏后氏之綏，殷之大白，周之大赤。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0012", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction", "source_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 12, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《明堂位》 12", "sort_key": "0012", "text_original": "夏后氏駱馬，黑鬣。殷人白馬，黑首。周人黃馬，蕃鬣。", "text_normalized": "夏后氏駱馬，黑鬣。殷人白馬，黑首。周人黃馬，蕃鬣。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0013", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction", "source_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 13, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《明堂位》 13", "sort_key": "0013", "text_original": "夏后氏，牲尚黑，殷白牡，周騂剛。", "text_normalized": "夏后氏，牲尚黑，殷白牡，周騂剛。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0014", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction", "source_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 14, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《明堂位》 14", "sort_key": "0014", "text_original": "泰，有虞氏之尊也。山罍，夏后氏之尊也。著，殷尊也。犧象，周尊也。", "text_normalized": "泰，有虞氏之尊也。山罍，夏后氏之尊也。著，殷尊也。犧象，周尊也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0015", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction", "source_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 15, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《明堂位》 15", "sort_key": "0015", "text_original": "爵，夏后氏以琖，殷以斝，周以爵。", "text_normalized": "爵，夏后氏以琖，殷以斝，周以爵。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0016", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction", "source_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 16, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《明堂位》 16", "sort_key": "0016", "text_original": "灌尊，夏后氏以雞夷。殷以斝，周以黃目。", "text_normalized": "灌尊，夏后氏以雞夷。殷以斝，周以黃目。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0017", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction", "source_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 17, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《明堂位》 17", "sort_key": "0017", "text_original": "其勺，夏后氏以龍勺，殷以疏勺，周以蒲勺。", "text_normalized": "其勺，夏后氏以龍勺，殷以疏勺，周以蒲勺。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0018", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction", "source_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 18, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《明堂位》 18", "sort_key": "0018", "text_original": "土鼓蕢桴葦龠，伊耆氏之樂也。拊搏玉磬揩擊，大琴大瑟，中琴小瑟，四代之樂器也。", "text_normalized": "土鼓蕢桴葦龠，伊耆氏之樂也。拊搏玉磬揩擊，大琴大瑟，中琴小瑟，四代之樂器也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0019", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction", "source_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 19, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《明堂位》 19", "sort_key": "0019", "text_original": "魯公之廟，文世室也。武公之廟，武世室也。", "text_normalized": "魯公之廟，文世室也。武公之廟，武世室也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0020", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction", "source_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 20, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《明堂位》 20", "sort_key": "0020", "text_original": "米廩，有虞氏之庠也；序，夏后氏之序也；瞽宗，殷學也；頖宮，周學也。", "text_normalized": "米廩，有虞氏之庠也；序，夏后氏之序也；瞽宗，殷學也；頖宮，周學也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0021", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction", "source_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 21, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《明堂位》 21", "sort_key": "0021", "text_original": "崇鼎，貫鼎，大璜，封父龜，天子之器也。越棘，大弓，天子之戎器也。", "text_normalized": "崇鼎，貫鼎，大璜，封父龜，天子之器也。越棘，大弓，天子之戎器也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0022", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction", "source_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 22, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《明堂位》 22", "sort_key": "0022", "text_original": "夏后氏之鼓，足。殷，楹鼓；周，縣鼓。垂之和鐘，叔之離磬，女媧之笙簧。", "text_normalized": "夏后氏之鼓，足。殷，楹鼓；周，縣鼓。垂之和鐘，叔之離磬，女媧之笙簧。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0023", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction", "source_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 23, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《明堂位》 23", "sort_key": "0023", "text_original": "夏后氏之龍簨虡，殷之崇牙，周之璧翣。", "text_normalized": "夏后氏之龍簨虡，殷之崇牙，周之璧翣。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0024", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction", "source_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 24, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《明堂位》 24", "sort_key": "0024", "text_original": "有虞氏之兩敦，夏后氏之四連，殷之六瑚，周之八簋。", "text_normalized": "有虞氏之兩敦，夏后氏之四連，殷之六瑚，周之八簋。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0025", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction", "source_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 25, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《明堂位》 25", "sort_key": "0025", "text_original": "俎，有虞氏以梡，夏后氏以嶡，殷以椇，周以房俎。", "text_normalized": "俎，有虞氏以梡，夏后氏以嶡，殷以椇，周以房俎。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0026", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction", "source_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 26, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《明堂位》 26", "sort_key": "0026", "text_original": "夏后氏以楬豆，殷玉豆，周獻豆。", "text_normalized": "夏后氏以楬豆，殷玉豆，周獻豆。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0027", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction", "source_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 27, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《明堂位》 27", "sort_key": "0027", "text_original": "有虞氏服韍，夏后氏山，殷火，周龍章。", "text_normalized": "有虞氏服韍，夏后氏山，殷火，周龍章。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0028", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction", "source_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 28, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《明堂位》 28", "sort_key": "0028", "text_original": "有虞氏祭首，夏后氏祭心，殷祭肝，周祭肺。", "text_normalized": "有虞氏祭首，夏后氏祭心，殷祭肝，周祭肺。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0029", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction", "source_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 29, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《明堂位》 29", "sort_key": "0029", "text_original": "夏后氏尚明水，殷尚醴，周尚酒。", "text_normalized": "夏后氏尚明水，殷尚醴，周尚酒。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0030", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction", "source_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 30, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《明堂位》 30", "sort_key": "0030", "text_original": "有虞氏官五十，夏后氏官百，殷二百，周三百。", "text_normalized": "有虞氏官五十，夏后氏官百，殷二百，周三百。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0031", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction", "source_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 31, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《明堂位》 31", "sort_key": "0031", "text_original": "有虞氏之綏，夏后氏之綢練，殷之崇牙，周之璧翣。", "text_normalized": "有虞氏之綏，夏后氏之綢練，殷之崇牙，周之璧翣。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0032", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction", "source_id": "liji-014-the-places-in-the-hall-of-distinction__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 32, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《明堂位》 32", "sort_key": "0032", "text_original": "凡四代之服、器、官，魯兼用之。是故，魯，王禮也，天下傳之久矣。君臣，未嘗相弒也；禮樂刑法政俗，未嘗相變也，天下以為有道之國。是故，天下資禮樂焉。", "text_normalized": "凡四代之服、器、官，魯兼用之。是故，魯，王禮也，天下傳之久矣。君臣，未嘗相弒也；禮樂刑法政俗，未嘗相變也，天下以為有道之國。是故，天下資禮樂焉。", "notes": ""}
